                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18331128-106-off597 t18331128-106-crimeloc600"></join>. The prisoner was in my employ for three months, and left on the 23rd of October; I had been ill for three months; on the day after he left me I began to arrange the goods in my window; I missed two or three hair brushes; in looking for them I missed some razors and nail brushes; and nine tortoiseshell combs, these are the articles produced by the pawnbroker, these are some of the razors I lost; I know this one in particular, by some ink spilt on it, and here is one hair brush, I can swear to it by a mark.</p>
